<html>
<head>
<title>Certificate {{.CourseName}} {{.Name}}</title>
</head>
<body>
<div style="width:100%px; height:620px; padding:20px; text-align:center; border: 10px solid #0D47A1">
<div style="width:98%px; height:580px; padding:20px; text-align:center; border: 5px solid #4CAF50;background-image: url('/data/icon.png');background-blend-mode: lighten;background-position: center;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: 35%;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">
       <span style="font-size:50px; font-weight:bold;font-family: sans-serif-light;">Certificate of Completion</span>
       <br><br>
       <span style="font-size:20px;font-family: sans-serif-light;"><i>This is to certify that</i></span>
       <br><br>
       <span style="font-size:40px;font-family: sans-serif-medium;"><b>{{.Name}}</b></span><br/><br/>
       <span style="font-size:20px;font-family: sans-serif-light;"><i>has completed the course</i></span> <br/><br/><br/>
       <span style="font-size:40px;font-family: sans-serif-medium;"><b>{{.CourseName}}</b></span><br/>
       <span style="font-size:20px;font-family: sans-serif-light;"><i>(provide by Lets Course)</i></span> <br/><br/>
       <span style="font-size:20px;font-family: sans-serif-light;"></span> <br/>
       <span style="font-size:15px;font-family: sans-serif-light;"><i>Issued on:</i></span><br>
       <span style="font-size:20px;font-family: sans-serif-light; font-weight:bold">{{.Date}}</span>
       <br><br><br><br>
       <span style="font-size:20px;font-family: sans-serif-light;"></span>Authenticity of this certificate can be validated by going to:</span><br/>
       <span style="font-size:15px;font-family: sans-serif-light"><a href="http://letscourse.com/cert/{{.HashID}}">http://letscourse.com/cert/{{.HashID}}</a></span>
</div>
</div>
<script src="https://www.google.com/cloudprint/client/cpgadget.js">
</script>
<script>
var printThis = {{.Print}};
if (printThis == "yes"){
       window.print();
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
